20 (12) For cool season lawn and turf grasses, the following
21 statements on the labeling:
22 (A) For single kinds of grasses, the name of the kind or the
23 kind and variety.
24 (B) For grass mixtures:
25 (i) the word "mix", "mixed", "mixture", or "blend" must be
