34 (C) The percentage by weight of agricultural seed other than
35 those required to be named on the label (which must be
36 designated as "crop seed").
37 (D) The percentage by weight of inert matter.
38 (E) The percentage by weight of all weed seeds. The
39 maximum weed seed content may not exceed two and
40 five-tenths percent (2.5%) by weight.
41 (F) The name and rate of occurrence per pound of each kind
42 of restricted noxious weed seed present and listed under the
2026 IN 1192—LS 6703/DI 148

10
1 heading "Noxious Weed Seeds". Restricted noxious weed seed
2 may not exceed twenty-five hundredths of one percent (0.25%)
3 by weight.
4 (G) For each agricultural seed named under clause (A) or (B),
5 the following:
6 (i) The percentage of germination, exclusive of hard seed.
